Package: flowdatacanada
Title: Provide access to spatially dispersed river flow datasets in Canada
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sam", "Albers", , "sam.albers@hakai.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hakai Institute", , role = "cph")
    )
Description: Provide access to spatially dispersed river flow datasets in Canada through 
    public APIs and data portals. This package simplifies the process of
    retrieving, cleaning, and analyzing river flow data for hydrological studies
    and environmental monitoring.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://hakaiinstitute.github.io/flowdatacanada/
